                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If a berberoka sees a crab or crab-like creature, the berberoka must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-traits=\"emotion, fear, mental\" data-pf2-label=\"Fear of Crabs DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"33\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-dc=\"33\" data-pf2-traits=\"mental,emotion,fear\" data-pf2-label=\"Fear of Crabs DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save. They then becomes immune to the sight of that creature for 10 minutes.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The berberoka is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The berberoka becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The berberoka gains the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fleeing]{Fleeing} condition for 1 round and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 4}.</p>"
