                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The berberoka is waterlogged.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The berberoka sprays a blast of water in a 60-foot line. All creatures in the line take [[/r 6d8 #bludgeoning]]{6d8 bludgeoning damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Spray Water DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"35\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save). On a failed save, a creature is knocked @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone} and pushed back 5 feet (10 feet on a critically failed save).</p>"
